"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-tatjana-smith-facts-paris-2024-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7679845677335133, \"rank\": 0.3018766513497441, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbMeet the real Tatjana: Team SA's Golden Girl at the Paris 2024 Olympics  Some fascinating insights here.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7679845677335133, \"rank\": 0.3018766513497441, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 237, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Girl_(film)\", \"score\": 0.7617510530200124, \"rank\": 0.2633744855966091, \"text\": \"Golden Girl\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Girl_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golden_Girl_(film)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smith has been a household name around South Africa for a while.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999993447091, \"rank\": 6.445342555711539e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, her antics at the Paris 2024 Olympics have taken things up a notch.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know she missed qualification for the 200m breaststroke at Rio 2016 by 0.01 seconds?\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Info viaolympics.com'sofficial website.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A personal highlight for Tanja was winning 200m breaststroke gold at the 2018 Commonwealth Games on the Gold Coast of Australia.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanja_von_Lahnstein\", \"score\": 0.9480720222188794, \"rank\": 0.05477218667390453, \"text\": \"Tanja\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanja_von_Lahnstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanja_von_Lahnstein\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.966565364822722, \"rank\": 0.03458873240317739, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having my parents in the stands with some of our family friends and winning my first major competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My love for swimming makes me want to get up every morning and go to training.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like my second home.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being fortunate enough to travel the world doing what I love, seeing new places and meeting new people and sports heroes, motivates me a lot.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important thing every young swimmer should realise is that nothing is impossible.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They only need to believe and be prepared to put in the long and hard hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When reflecting on missing out on the 200m breaststroke in Rio, Smith was typically philosophical and upbeat about one of the biggest setbacks in her professional career.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999967729383799, \"rank\": 3.2270718741005723e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"2016 was a bit of a disappointment, but I knew everything happens for a reason.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't ready at that time.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We got our hopes up and then I kind of got a dip, creating all that expectation.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My fall was quite big, and I had to try and fall in love with the sport again.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, maybe I needed to go through that disappointment to take me where I was in 2021 - more of a confident swimmer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smithstands to become only the second swimmer in history after Penny Heyns in 1996 to complete the 100m and 200m breaststroke golden double at the same Olympics event.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Penny Heyns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wasn't yet born when Heyns accomplished this historic feat.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old cruised through her 200m breaststroke heat and has qualified for the semi-final.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That will go onWednesday 31 July between 21:51 and 21:58.\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The finalis onThursday 01 August at 21:04.You know thatNando's will be watching.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith won this event in Tokyo with a time of2.18.95, a world record which has since been eclipsed by Russian Evgeniia Chikunova in 2023 with a time of2.17.55.Will she take her record back?\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999752445709538, \"rank\": 2.475314822943096e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2390, \"end\": 2397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.7811558563479428, \"rank\": 0.2801423737531602, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evgeniia_Chikunova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evgeniia Chikunova\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evgeniia_Chikunova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http